== Extreme points ==

This is a list of the extreme points of [[Cameroon]], the points that are farther north, south, east or west than any other location.

* Northern-most point - unnamed [[peninsula]] jutting into [[lake Chad]], [[Far North Province|Far North]] province
* Eastern-most point - unnamed location on the border with the [[Republic of Congo]] in the [[Sangha river]] opposite the Congolese town of [[Bomassa]], [[East Region (Cameroon)|East]] region
* Southern-most point - unnamed headland at the [[confluence]] on the [[Sangha river]] and the [[Ngoko river]] immediately north of the Congolese town of [[Ouesso]], [[East Region (Cameroon)|East]] region
* Western-most point - unnamed point on [[Akwabana island]], [[Southwest region (Cameroon)|Southwest]] region

