==Cameroonian Air Force==

The Cameroon Air Force has 34 aircraft including 11 helicopters. The air force has bases in [[Garoua]], [[Koutaba]], [[Yaounde]], [[Douala]] and [[Bamenda]]. The Cameroonian Air Force was founded in 1960 the year of independence form France.There are around 300 troops in the air force.

